<title>GERMANY: Bundesbank details M3 developments in May.</title>
<headline>Bundesbank details M3 developments in May.</headline>
<dateline>FRANKFURT 1997-06-20</dateline>
<text>
<p>The Bundesbank published the following data relating to M3 money supply in May.</p>
<p>AGGREGATE (in bln marks)	  May97  Apr97  May96  End-May</p>
<p>								     Level</p>
